00:04.438 --> 00:06.074
- Jonah! Oh, we love you!

00:06.107 --> 00:07.608
- I'm Jonah.
- Maddie.

00:09.343 --> 00:10.611
- You're gonna like fly me
home, to Nashville?

00:10.644 --> 00:12.580
- Well, actually,
my pilot will, but yeah.

00:12.613 --> 00:14.548
- Totally.

