on you later.

00:41.142 --> 00:42.110
- Hey.
- Yeah. Hey.

00:44.812 --> 00:47.815
- Well, you know how much
I care about this company.

00:47.848 --> 00:51.219
And, uh, you know how much
respect I have for you.

00:51.252 --> 00:52.820
