03:46.960 --> 03:47.595
Why?

03:47.628 --> 03:49.830
Hey, whoa, whoa, whoa. Why?

03:53.634 --> 03:56.970
- Hey.
- Hey.

03:57.004 --> 03:59.607
Hello.
- Hello.

