04:03.577 --> 04:05.546
I couldn't remember if--oh.

04:05.579 --> 04:07.281
- That's perfect.
- Great.

04:07.315 --> 04:08.282
- It was good.

04:08.316 --> 04:09.650
It was good.

04:09.683 --> 04:11.419
I went to Vanderbilt,
and I wanted to see

04:11.452 --> 04:14.021
