a song a little bit. So...

04:21.094 --> 04:22.363
- Busy day.
- Yeah.

04:22.396 --> 04:23.864
- When do I get
to hear the song?

04:23.897 --> 04:27.568
- Soon. Right now
it's a bit of a mess, so...

04:27.601 --> 04:29.303
- I'm sure
it's a beautiful mess.

04:30.604 --> 04:33.040
- Sorry.

04:33.073 --> 04:37.411
- I don't know.
I'm just, uh, I don't know.

04:38.679 --> 04:40.614
- Yeah, well,
I'm right there with you.

04:40.648 --> 04:43.050
- You know, Jake asked me
where I was the other day.

04:43.083 --> 04:45.519
