know what to say.

04:45.553 --> 04:48.389
- Maybe we don't need
to say anything

04:48.422 --> 04:49.790
quite yet to the kids.

04:49.823 --> 04:52.760
You know, until we figure out
what we're doing here.

04:52.793 --> 04:54.795
- Yeah. That sounds good.

04:54.828 --> 04:57.331
Okay.

04:57.365 --> 05:00.468
