a good idea, too.

05:00.501 --> 05:02.770
- Daphne. Hey.
- Dad.

05:02.803 --> 05:04.538
- Hello, Louisa.
Hi, guys.

05:04.572 --> 05:05.539
- Hey.

05:05.573 --> 05:07.841
- Hey.
- Give me a hug.

05:07.875 --> 05:09.443
