05:27.027 --> 05:28.696
- Yeah. Looks like
we're doing it that way.

05:28.729 --> 05:29.797
- Yeah.

05:40.508 --> 05:42.109
- School.

05:42.142 --> 05:43.677
You know, that thing
that's legally required.

05:43.711 --> 05:45.045
- No, no, no.
Let me make you some breakfast.

05:45.078 --> 05:46.780
Most important meal of the day.
- Granola bar.

05:46.814 --> 05:48.449
- That--that is not breakfast.

05:48.482 --> 05:49.917
- It says breakfast
right there on the package.

05:49.950 --> 05:51.151
- Okay.
Daph--Daphne, wait.

05:52.285 --> 05:54.755
- You know you can talk
to me about anything, right?

05:54.788 --> 05:56.624
You know that?

05:56.657 --> 05:57.758
- Yeah, I know.

05:59.460 --> 06:01.061
- Yesterday at the coffee shop,
I thought that maybe we could--

06:01.094 --> 06:02.396
- Carpool's here.
I'm sorry, I really have to go.

06:02.430 --> 06:03.664
- Hold on.
Wait, wait, wait.

06:04.865 --> 06:05.666
