to get into college?

06:07.034 --> 06:08.636
- Go.
- Thank you.

06:10.804 --> 06:13.173
- Avery, welcome.
I'm so glad to meet you.

06:13.206 --> 06:16.444
- Same here.
I've heard great things.

06:16.477 --> 06:17.845
- Juliette, Laura was
hoping to go over

06:17.878 --> 06:19.447
this week's volunteer
schedule with you.

06:19.480 --> 06:20.781
Perhaps I'll show
Avery around a bit,

06:20.814 --> 06:22.950
then we can meet
back up later.

06:22.983 --> 06:24.685
- Sounds good.
- Okay.

06:26.687 --> 06:28.822
- We're heading to one of my
favorite parts of the campus:

06:28.856 --> 06:31.792
The meditation garden.
- That sounds peaceful.

06:31.825 --> 06:33.761
I can see why Juliette
likes it here.

06:33.794 --> 06:36.564
- It's amazing how far she's
come in a short amount of time.

06:36.597 --> 06:38.666
Isn't it?

06:38.699 --> 06:43.103
- The way she's allowing herself
to be more honest, more present.

06:43.136 --> 06:45.973
She's been stuck in
a self-destructive pattern

06:46.006 --> 06:48.208
for so long,
it's remarkable how open

06:48.241 --> 06:51.178
she's become to the possibility
of something better.

06:51.211 --> 06:53.714
- Well, she's
a remarkable person.

06:53.747 --> 06:57.017
- Look, I understand you
being protective of her.

06:57.050 --> 07:00.721
Just know I'm not trying
to be some kind of guru.

07:00.754 --> 07:01.855
I hate that word.

07:01.889 --> 07:03.491
I--I don't have all the answers.

07:03.524 --> 07:06.026
I can only speak from
what I know to be true.

07:06.059 --> 07:09.497
Even after decades of
practicing coherent philosophy.

07:09.530 --> 07:13.634
- So what is coherent
philosophy exactly?

07:13.667 --> 07:15.503
I mean, you... you came up
with it, right?

07:15.536 --> 07:16.737
- I refined the technique.

07:16.770 --> 07:20.140
And I've certainly brought
the message to a wide audience.

07:20.173 --> 07:23.511
But the ideas behind
the movement are far older

07:23.544 --> 07:26.980
than you or I, perhaps older
than civilization itself.

07:28.048 --> 07:29.683
- Yeah.

07:29.717 --> 07:31.652
- Okay. Just lift with
your legs or something.

07:31.685 --> 07:33.987
- I been lifting with my legs
since before you were born.

07:34.021 --> 07:35.556
- Ah, shut up.

07:37.057 --> 07:39.026
- You know when you
just kind of need a change?

07:39.059 --> 07:41.695
- Yeah, in theory, I guess.

07:41.729 --> 07:43.864
Me, I could use
a little less change.

07:43.897 --> 07:45.799
Between Zach leaving, and...

07:48.068 --> 07:49.737
- Is everything okay
with Jessie?

07:49.770 --> 07:51.572
- Yeah, yeah.
I mean, they have been.

07:51.605 --> 07:52.873
Just Daphne.

07:54.942 --> 07:57.678
- No, no, she just saw us out.

07:57.711 --> 08:00.113
I didn't know what to say
so I played it off.

08:01.314 --> 08:03.551
You know, now,
she says she's fine.

08:03.584 --> 08:04.752
She doesn't want
to go into it.

08:04.785 --> 08:06.019
- Ugh.

08:06.053 --> 08:09.056
Well, maybe she just needs some
time to process it on her own.

08:09.089 --> 08:11.859
- She's been through so much.

08:11.892 --> 08:15.929
How can I add to that?
Just... feels selfish.

08:15.963 --> 08:17.297
- Oh, okay.

08:17.330 --> 08:18.732
That is the last word
I would ever use with you,

08:18.766 --> 08:20.568
especially in regards
to those girls.

08:20.601 --> 08:22.102
You do everything
that's best for them,

08:22.135 --> 08:24.071
and you keep them happy.

08:24.104 --> 08:27.775
You're a person, too.

08:27.808 --> 08:29.209
You deserve to be loved.

08:29.242 --> 08:33.146
That might not be what this is,
but what if it could be?

08:34.982 --> 08:37.084
- I like her, like, a lot,
you know,

08:37.117 --> 08:39.787
but sometimes
when we're together,

08:39.820 --> 08:40.788
it just feels...

08:42.155 --> 08:43.824
I don't know, strange.

08:43.857 --> 08:45.058
You know? Wrong.

08:48.128 --> 08:50.097
She's not Rayna.
- Yeah.

08:54.134 --> 08:55.869
- Maybe I'm not ready.

08:58.138 --> 09:00.073
- That makes sense.

09:00.107 --> 09:06.079
The thing is, you might not
ever feel ready.

09:06.113 --> 09:09.016
Completely.

09:09.049 --> 09:11.118
- Oh, thanks, that makes me
feel a lot better.

09:11.151 --> 09:12.686
- You know what I mean.

09:24.698 --> 09:26.667
