35:22.688 --> 35:24.556
A ton of guys
at the gym take it.

35:24.590 --> 35:28.227
- I'm sure they are, but that's
not all you're taking.

35:28.260 --> 35:29.161
- Uh...

35:31.663 --> 35:34.400
I was taking some steroids,
but I stopped.

35:34.433 --> 35:35.834
- Well, they're still
in your system.

35:35.867 --> 35:38.404
You've got to stop now.

35:38.437 --> 35:41.907
I can help you with a plan to
get your body regulated again.

35:43.642 --> 35:47.346
- Okay. I get it.
I do.

