36:02.228 --> 36:04.496
- No, he's at his dad's.

36:04.530 --> 36:07.599
- I just--I felt awful about
what happened on the phone.

36:07.633 --> 36:09.835
- You don't have
to say anything.

36:09.868 --> 36:12.538
- Well, it's what
I didn't say, Jessie.

36:12.571 --> 36:14.840
Truth is, Daphne's fine.

36:14.873 --> 36:16.608
Or she's going to be.

36:16.642 --> 36:18.610
It's me. I'm the one
