to wreck this thing,

36:24.283 --> 36:25.651
but I don't know how I can't.

36:26.985 --> 36:28.687
Would that take some
of the pressure off?

36:28.720 --> 36:30.556
- Yeah, it might.
Could we do it that way?

36:30.589 --> 36:32.491
- Yeah.

36:33.859 --> 36:36.495
- Look, Deacon, I understand
if you're not ready

36:36.528 --> 36:37.563
and that's totally fine.

36:37.596 --> 36:38.964
I just need you
to tell me that,

36:38.997 --> 36:40.966
