37:24.876 --> 37:26.678
- Nothing, nothing.

37:28.046 --> 37:29.848
- You wouldn't understand.

37:29.881 --> 37:32.951
- Okay, maybe not,
but I'll always listen.

37:32.984 --> 37:35.787
- How are you so okay
with him dating her?

37:37.589 --> 37:39.391
- It's not that
I'm okay with it.

37:39.425 --> 37:41.427
I just--I don't want him
to be lonely.

37:42.694 --> 37:43.962
- No, of course I don't.

37:46.565 --> 37:48.300
- You can't tell him
I said anything.

37:50.602 --> 37:51.703
Maddie.

37:51.737 --> 37:53.905
Okay, I won't.
I promise.

37:56.675 --> 37:59.811
- I meant what I said

37:59.845 --> 38:02.781
